    %li.main__adCarousel__third
      .main__adCarousel__third__content
        %h2
          だれでもかんたん、人生を変えるフリマアプリ
        %p
          今すぐ無料ダウンロード！
        .main__adCarousel__third__content__link
          = link_to "#" do
            %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/app-store-9c5e28e8f81bd9912e0ded2f78821e04778a1356c05dc7c7bf1e88614be37c34.svg", width: "170px"}
          = link_to "#" do
            %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/google-play-469c63f1269e456307c4dde176b33cc3bbbbf142ac4d7369656010130149db1a.svg", width: "170px"}

  .main__firstIntro
    %h1.subTitle
      FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
    %ul.main__firstIntro__lists
      %li.main__firstIntro__lists__list
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__pict
          %span.number 1
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/pict-reason-01.jpg"}
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__text
          %span 3分
          ですぐに出品
        %p スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる!
        
      %li.main__firstIntro__lists__list
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__pict
          %span.number 2
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/pict-reason-02.jpg"}
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__text
          %span シンプル
          で使いやすい
        %p めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ!

      %li.main__firstIntro__lists__list--last
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__pict
          %span.number 3
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/pict-reason-03.jpg"}
        .main__firstIntro__lists__list__text
          手数料
          %span 業界最安
        %p 最大3%でお得に出品&購入!

  .main__pickup
    %h1 ピックアップカテゴリー
    .main__pickup__title
      %h2
        新規投稿商品
      .main__pickup__title__productLists
        = render @products
    - console
  .main__secondIntro
    %h2.subTitle
      FURIMAの特徴
    .main__secondIntro__lists
      %section.main__secondIntro__lists__list
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__pict
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/icon-01.png"}
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__text
          簡単に売り買いできる
          %p スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
    
      %section.main__secondIntro__lists__list
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__pict
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/icon-03.png"}
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__text
          売上金は即日振込みに対応
          %p 午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
      
      %section.main__secondIntro__lists__list
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__pict
          %img{src: "https://lasttask2020.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/icon-04.png"}
        .main__secondIntro__lists__list__text
          様々な支払いに対応
          %p お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。


